1
00:00:03,070 --> 00:00:03,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will...</font>

2
00:00:05,740 --> 00:00:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll always be by your side.</font>

3
00:00:27,980 --> 00:00:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will!</font>

4
00:00:39,230 --> 00:00:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rosty! Rosty!</font>

5
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rosty!</font>

6
00:00:59,370 --> 00:01:00,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Ice Faction Aide-de-Camp 
<font size="22">Sarissa Alfeld</font></font></b></font></font>

7
00:01:01,170 --> 00:01:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Lightning Faction Aide-de-Camp 
<font size="22">Guilford Zurgas</font></font></b></font></font>

8
00:01:03,230 --> 00:01:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lord Zeo!</font>

9
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And where are you planning on going, Zeo?</font>

10
00:01:06,380 --> 00:01:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="20">Cariot Incindia Wiseman</font></b></font></font>

11
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's obvious, isn't it? The battlefield.</font>

12
00:01:12,010 --> 00:01:15,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crying and wailing,
dying pathetically by the wayside...</font>

13
00:01:15,420 --> 00:01:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every last one of them is useless!</font>

14
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

15
00:01:20,710 --> 00:01:22,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The most useless of all...</font>

16
00:01:20,850 --> 00:01:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="20">Zeo Thorzeus Reinbolt</font></b></font></font>

17
00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:25,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}are us for sitting here 
and watching them die!</font>

18
00:01:26,250 --> 00:01:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lord Aaron has already explained.</font>

19
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}If we, the Magia Vander, fall, 
the Great Barrier will vanish.</font>

20
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="20">Aaron Masterias Oldking</font></b></font></font>

21
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that event, there is but one outcome.</font>

22
00:01:36,130 --> 00:01:40,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Celestial Host will utterly 
destroy this world, reducing it to ash.</font>

23
00:01:40,390 --> 00:01:42,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cowardly flames...</font>

24
00:01:42,780 --> 00:01:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the moment, even we are at 
a disadvantage against those things.</font>

25
00:01:46,340 --> 00:01:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should at least wait until 
our magical energy has recovered.</font>

26
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ought to be more conscious of
your position as a Magia Vander, Zeo.</font>

27
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm always telling you that, aren't I?</font>

28
00:01:56,190 --> 00:01:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, come back and take your seat.</font>

29
00:01:57,930 --> 00:02:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want me to be more conscious?</font>

30
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, screw this.</font>

31
00:02:02,110 --> 00:02:04,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can keep your feeble Wand title.</font>

32
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to get back here.</font>

33
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:15,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't, it will become necessary 
to pin you in place by force.</font>

34
00:02:17,370 --> 00:02:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go ahead and try it.</font>

35
00:02:20,370 --> 00:02:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Elf Faction Aide-de-Camp
<font size="22">Lefiya Viridis</font></font></b></font></font>

36
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This may turn into
a disgraceful spectacle.</font>

37
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would you like to do, Lady Ellenor?</font>

38
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This is preposterous.</font>

39
00:02:27,250 --> 00:02:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="20">Ellenor Ljos Alf</font></b></font></font>

40
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I shall remain a spectator.</font>

41
00:02:29,890 --> 00:02:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}After all, this is the mages' land.</font>

42
00:02:32,270 --> 00:02:35,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}There is one of our 
kindred at the academy.</font>

43
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:35,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Elf Faction Aide-de-Camp
<font size="22">Filvis Challia</font></font></b></font></font>

44
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would you have us do?</font>

45
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go.</font>

46
00:02:41,410 --> 00:02:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

47
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:46,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The battle above ground 
is already desperate.</i></font>

48
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the Magia Vander just 
aren't in step with each other.</i></font>

49
00:02:49,530 --> 00:02:50,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If things continue this way...</i></font>

50
00:02:52,990 --> 00:02:54,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Wait...</font>

51
00:02:54,740 --> 00:02:56,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Elfaria?</font>

52
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:03,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="20">Elfaria Albis Serfort</font></b></font></font>

53
00:03:00,390 --> 00:03:02,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Rescind your order.</font>

54
00:03:02,350 --> 00:03:03,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We're wasting time.</font>

55
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will not change my mind.</font>

56
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stand down, Elfaria.</font>

57
00:03:26,310 --> 00:03:31,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to save those 
who are dear to me, including Will.</font>

58
00:03:31,670 --> 00:03:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you get in my way, 
I will knock you down as well.</font>

59
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:38,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-L-Lady... Lady Elfaria?!</font>

60
00:04:00,010 --> 00:04:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="12"><font color="#0d0a12">Episode 15
One Single Magic Spell</font></font></font></font>

61
00:05:17,210 --> 00:05:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The Devander's arrival has spelled
the collapse of our front line.</i></font>

62
00:05:17,380 --> 00:05:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy Professor
<font size="22">Workner Norgram</font></font></b></font></font>

63
00:05:20,490 --> 00:05:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the surviving Dinoboroses 
are starting to drive back our mages.</i></font>

64
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even the dwarves can't keep 
this situation in check.</i></font>

65
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This boy is our last and only hope.</i></font>

66
00:05:32,150 --> 00:05:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...can't.</font>

67
00:05:34,550 --> 00:05:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't protect anything.</font>

68
00:05:36,990 --> 00:05:38,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't save anything.</font>

69
00:05:38,940 --> 00:05:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't do anything!</font>

70
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just like it was back then.</font>

71
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is no different than when 
they took Elfie away!</font>

72
00:05:50,030 --> 00:05:52,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it because I can't use magic?</font>

73
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I can't use magic, I can't 
protect Elfie, or Rosty, or anyone else!</font>

74
00:05:59,070 --> 00:06:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all because I'm just a laggard!</font>

75
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:05,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of it! Everything! 
It's all because of that!</font>

76
00:06:07,910 --> 00:06:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will, calm down!</font>

77
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Professor Workner.</font>

78
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why am I...</font>

79
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is it just me?!</font>

80
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why am I the only one who can't use magic?</font>

81
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will! Pull yourself together!</font>

82
00:06:26,090 --> 00:06:27,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will!</font>

83
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yo.</font>

84
00:06:30,490 --> 00:06:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That brat reeks.</font>

85
00:06:32,450 --> 00:06:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's even more of a pain than the dwarves.</font>

86
00:06:34,540 --> 00:06:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what his stench is telling me.</font>

87
00:06:38,210 --> 00:06:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill you both at once.</font>

88
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Colette!</font>

89
00:06:57,810 --> 00:06:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy, Sixth Year
<font size="22">Lihanna Owenzaus</font></font></b></font></font>

90
00:06:58,030 --> 00:06:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Colette, what are you doing?</font>

91
00:07:00,230 --> 00:07:02,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy, Sixth Year
<font size="22">Colette Loire</font></font></b></font></font>

92
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Just now, that was...</font>

93
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Familiar
<font size="22"> Kiki</font></font></b></font></font>

94
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Kiki!</font>

95
00:07:05,330 --> 00:07:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kiki, are you all right?</font>

96
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be... Just now, was that Will?</font>

97
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, Kiki! Take me to Will!</font>

98
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sion?</font>

99
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You guys figure out 
what to do about all this!</font>

100
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy 
<font size="22">Julius Reinberg</font></font></b></font></font>

101
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}H-Hey!</font>

102
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Julius, make some doubles of yourself!</font>

103
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:30,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Huh?</font>

104
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Julius, hurry!</font>

105
00:07:31,710 --> 00:07:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What?!</font>

106
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy, Sixth Year
<font size="22">Wignall Lindor</font></font></b></font></font>

107
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hurry up and do it, Julius!</font>

108
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Aren't they ready yet, Julius?</font>

109
00:07:35,690 --> 00:07:36,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Julius!</font>

110
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The whole lot of you! Stop treating me 
like I'm at your convenience!</font>

111
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That silly Marze 
seems to be quite excited.</i></font>

112
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:52,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A chorus of screams 
in a monsters' march...</i></font>

113
00:07:52,940 --> 00:07:56,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This delightful melody 
will continue forever!</i></font>

114
00:07:56,480 --> 00:08:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, how I'd love to go 
 hunt some adorable heads.</i></font>

115
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But unfortunately, today 
my job is to be the conductor.</i></font>

116
00:08:04,670 --> 00:08:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now, you should be on your way, too.</i></font>

117
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is bad.</i></font>

118
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's headed for the tower.</i></font>

119
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't let it get near Central Flos, 
the heart of the city!</font>

120
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That monster is capable 
of killing the Magia Vander!</i></font>

121
00:08:26,650 --> 00:08:29,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="20">Clairie Serah</font></b></font></font>

122
00:08:33,410 --> 00:08:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serah!</font>

123
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Launch a suicide attack, dwarves!</font>

124
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make for the city center!</font>

125
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Destroy that mage slayer the Devander 
is using by any means necessary!</font>

126
00:08:44,180 --> 00:08:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't be serious!</font>

127
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My people are already battered and ragged 
from serving as shields for your kind!</font>

128
00:08:49,620 --> 00:08:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Donnan and the others have fallen!</font>

129
00:08:51,470 --> 00:08:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And you're telling us to go die?!</font>

130
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="20">Gina</font></b></font></font>

131
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes, I am!</font>

132
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy Professor
<font size="22">Edward Serfence</font></font></b></font></font>

133
00:08:56,460 --> 00:08:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the sake of the capital!</font>

134
00:08:58,380 --> 00:09:00,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To protect the children!</font>

135
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:02,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give your lives, dwarves!</font>

136
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gina!</font>

137
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Saeva Fulminas!</font>

138
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You... Why did you do that?</font>

139
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:33,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're up against an enemy 
impervious to magic, so right now...</font>

140
00:09:33,030 --> 00:09:36,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my life is worth 
far less than any of yours.</font>

141
00:09:37,170 --> 00:09:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all.</font>

142
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will pay the same price.</font>

143
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:45,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So please, lay down your lives!</font>

144
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Men!</font>

145
00:09:50,490 --> 00:09:52,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gather our brothers!</font>

146
00:09:52,610 --> 00:09:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We make for the city center!</font>

147
00:09:55,090 --> 00:09:56,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frubas Julier!</font>

148
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:02,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wait, Colette!</font>

149
00:10:01,830 --> 00:10:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy, Sixth Year 
<font size="22">Sion Ulster</font></font></b></font></font>

150
00:10:02,640 --> 00:10:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Don't run off alone!</font>

151
00:10:03,830 --> 00:10:05,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if we don't hurry, Will could be...</font>

152
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That laggard! 
He's always jerking us around!</font>

153
00:10:12,850 --> 00:10:14,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stear Viola!</font>

154
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Loire Sique!</font>

155
00:10:24,270 --> 00:10:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, of all times?!</font>

156
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Colette!</font>

157
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:35,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The western front line has fallen!</font>

158
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:38,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The high mage units in the
 northeast have been wiped out!</font>

159
00:10:38,330 --> 00:10:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Dinoboroses can't be stopped!</font>

160
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Send all civilians south!</font>

161
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Organo's team, the lightning faction, 
are holding the enemy at bay!</font>

162
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All units, keep fighting!</font>

163
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:50,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I repeat! Everyone out there, 
resist to the bitter end!</font>

164
00:10:50,850 --> 00:10:53,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Resist to the bitter end?</font>

165
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's gonna be impossible.</font>

166
00:10:57,820 --> 00:11:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder where Colette ended up.</font>

167
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:04,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would've liked to see 
her one last time...</font>

168
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy, Sixth Year 
<font size="22">Rose Prehnite</font></font></b></font></font>

169
00:11:05,430 --> 00:11:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}but it looks like things 
might be too far gone for that.</font>

170
00:11:08,190 --> 00:11:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy, Sixth Year 
<font size="22">Mike Maius</font></font></b></font></font>

171
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Everyone, head south!</font>

172
00:11:10,110 --> 00:11:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just follow the streets, 
and you'll get there in no time!</font>

173
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:14,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry!</font>

174
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've shouted too much. 
My throat can't take anymore.</font>

175
00:11:17,050 --> 00:11:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We can't go this way!</font>

176
00:11:18,460 --> 00:11:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Where are we supposed to go?</font>

177
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go south!</font>

178
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ignis Rooks!</font>

179
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lyril!</font>

180
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:31,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up! We're getting out of here!</font>

181
00:11:31,250 --> 00:11:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... But what about...</font>

182
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:37,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}He saved us, and we're the ones 
who get away?! That's just...</font>

183
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy, Sixth Year 
<font size="22">Lyril Mars</font></font></b></font></font>

184
00:11:37,220 --> 00:11:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy, Sixth Year 
<font size="22">Gordon Vally</font></font></b></font></font>

185
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit it with the heroics
 when your knees are knocking!</font>

186
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ulverre.</font>

187
00:11:54,530 --> 00:11:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Professor Eliza?</font>

188
00:11:56,780 --> 00:11:58,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Transport the wounded.</font>

189
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy Professor
<font size="22">Eliza Nosferat</font></font></b></font></font>

190
00:11:58,690 --> 00:12:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You will not pathetically flee.</font>

191
00:12:02,270 --> 00:12:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is aid that only you can provide!</font>

192
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave here to me and go!</font>

193
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, professor!</font>

194
00:12:12,460 --> 00:12:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're a handful.</font>

195
00:12:14,730 --> 00:12:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

196
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they are my darling students, after all.</font>

197
00:12:30,730 --> 00:12:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emma!</font>

198
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing? 
We need to get away from here already!</font>

199
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:35,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This girl...</font>

200
00:12:36,090 --> 00:12:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said she has a much 
younger brother back home.</font>

201
00:12:39,850 --> 00:12:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said she was finally 
going to see him.</font>

202
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now... It's too cruel!</font>

203
00:12:46,370 --> 00:12:48,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy, Sixth Year 
<font size="22">Emma Klever</font></font></b></font></font>

204
00:12:47,090 --> 00:12:48,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This is just too cruel!</font>

205
00:12:58,340 --> 00:12:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Edward is injured!</font>

206
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we've lost touch with Workner!</font>

207
00:13:01,490 --> 00:13:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Clairie, give us a situation report!</font>

208
00:13:04,050 --> 00:13:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Clairie, respond!</font>

209
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fires in the developments keep spreading!</font>

210
00:13:08,740 --> 00:13:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We can't guide the residents to evacuate!</font>

211
00:13:09,060 --> 00:13:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The situation couldn't be worse.</i></font>

212
00:13:09,230 --> 00:13:14,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Rigarden Magical Academy Headmistress
<font size="22">Caldron Anouve</font></font></b></font></font>

213
00:13:11,060 --> 00:13:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's taking all we have just 
to defend the civilians.</i></font>

214
00:13:11,060 --> 00:13:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Someone please come and help!</font>

215
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}East is taking heavy damage!</font>

216
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We can't turn the enemy back.</i></font>

217
00:13:13,970 --> 00:13:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Requesting backup!</font>

218
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The Devander is still alive and well!</font>

219
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:19,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And the horde of Dinoboroses 
is headed for the city center!</font>

220
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I-It's no good! We can't stop them!</font>

221
00:13:21,110 --> 00:13:24,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thanks to the dwarves, we've been able 
to whittle away at the mage slayers.</i></font>

222
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:25,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}My arm! My arm is...</font>

223
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But we can't stop the Devander.</i></font>

224
00:13:25,140 --> 00:13:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Reinforcements! 
Please send reinforcements!</font>

225
00:13:27,860 --> 00:13:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the heart 
of the dilemma on every front.</i></font>

226
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="14">Wizard's Tower Watcher
<font size="22">Iris Churchill</font></font></b></font></font>

227
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We can't hold them off any longer!</font>

228
00:13:30,060 --> 00:13:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Someone! Anyone, please!</font>

229
00:13:30,180 --> 00:13:32,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We can't scrape together 
enough of a fighting force!</i></font>

230
00:13:32,590 --> 00:13:36,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With only a few of the dwarves left, the 
best we can hope for is to die honorably.</i></font>

231
00:13:32,630 --> 00:13:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The southwest sector can't 
take any more! What should we—</font>

232
00:13:36,570 --> 00:13:39,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}H-Help us!</font>

233
00:13:36,580 --> 00:13:38,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At this rate, the tower will fall.</i></font>

234
00:13:39,070 --> 00:13:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What can we do?</i></font>

235
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The enemy is...</font>

236
00:13:43,890 --> 00:13:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is that?!</font>

237
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

238
00:13:46,930 --> 00:13:49,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, give me a situation report!</font>

239
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's happened?!</font>

240
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:55,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iris, how's the sword?</font>

241
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

242
00:13:57,060 --> 00:13:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're...</font>

243
00:14:04,770 --> 00:14:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is the sword right now?</font>

244
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="10"><font color="#c4af9b"><b>Yellow Mud Wand</b></font></font></font></font>

245
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="10"><b>{\an9}<u><font color="#5f2f0c">Rose Prehnite</font></u>

Race: Rhizanth   Age: 16   Height: 159 cm
Birthday: 3rd of Ahzomoon
Likes: Meat soup, curry, beef stew, Colette
Dislikes: Annoying adults
Wants to Protect: Colette Loire 

Deepest Dungeon Floor Reached: 8th
Equipment: Yellow Mud wand
Skills: Up to intermediate earth magic;
Plenus Witch


















An earth mage in the same academic year as Will 
and the others. Colette Loire's roommate. 
Easily talented and capable enough to ascend to
 the tower, but she hides it. If she's ever discovered,
 Lihanna would swiftly fall into a deep depression.
 Approached Colette on her grandfather's orders, 
but at this point she's changed from "an observation 
target" to "a friend dearer than any other."</b></font></font></font>

246
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="10"><b><u><font color="#5f2f0c">Devander</font></u>

<font size="8">A notorious monster from floor 40.
Though their overall numbers are small, they appear in the dungeon every few years.
Their ilk have killed Magia Vander of previous generations, and their strength 
surpasses even that of a floor keeper.

The tower has determined them to be worth 4,444 credits.</font></b></font></font></font>

247
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That guy... He's pretty good.</font>

248
00:14:23,660 --> 00:14:27,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imagine being in that situation and 
trying to return a killing blow.</font>

249
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I hit deep.</font>

250
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the end for him.</font>

251
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where am I?</font>

252
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The city. The west side.</font>

253
00:14:44,930 --> 00:14:47,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It appears we crashed.</font>

254
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was all I could do... to protect you.</font>

255
00:15:02,470 --> 00:15:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Professor... Workner...</font>

256
00:15:12,060 --> 00:15:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will, I'm sorry.</font>

257
00:15:15,280 --> 00:15:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only thing I can do now... 
is depend on you.</font>

258
00:15:20,540 --> 00:15:22,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the only one...</font>

259
00:15:23,130 --> 00:15:24,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But since it's you, I just know...</font>

260
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you can save this city.</font>

261
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't.</font>

262
00:15:30,790 --> 00:15:32,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't, Professor Workner.</font>

263
00:15:33,390 --> 00:15:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I let Rosty die. And now you, 
Professor Workner...</font>

264
00:15:38,470 --> 00:15:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone's always saving <i>me</i>.</font>

265
00:15:40,750 --> 00:15:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't protect the people 
who matter to me!</font>

266
00:15:44,830 --> 00:15:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't change a thing.</font>

267
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:50,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A sword can't overturn 
the order of the world!</font>

268
00:15:51,010 --> 00:15:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not...</font>

269
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:55,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone like me who can't
 even use magic isn't...</font>

270
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will, as your teacher...</font>

271
00:16:15,390 --> 00:16:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been lying to you.</font>

272
00:16:19,410 --> 00:16:20,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You...</font>

273
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You <i>can</i> use magic.</font>

274
00:16:25,350 --> 00:16:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll show everyone that there's hope.</font>

275
00:16:28,370 --> 00:16:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One single magic... spell...</font>

276
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. Please, wait!</font>

277
00:16:40,310 --> 00:16:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't die, Professor Workner!</font>

278
00:16:43,060 --> 00:16:47,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please tell me! What is my magic?!</font>

279
00:16:49,370 --> 00:16:50,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even the tiniest bit of gumption</font>

280
00:16:51,830 --> 00:16:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a light that can pierce anything...</font>

281
00:16:54,580 --> 00:16:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An argent light.</font>

282
00:16:58,260 --> 00:17:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're... Mister Finn.</font>

283
00:17:01,410 --> 00:17:02,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's all right.</font>

284
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:07,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once his pulse kicks in, 
he'll breathe again.</font>

285
00:17:07,590 --> 00:17:08,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

286
00:17:12,630 --> 00:17:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's more important right now is you.</font>

287
00:17:15,510 --> 00:17:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?</font>

288
00:17:17,330 --> 00:17:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and get on your feet.</font>

289
00:17:19,190 --> 00:17:21,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The stage has already 
been set for you, hasn't it?</font>

290
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An argent light?</font>

291
00:17:24,580 --> 00:17:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, before that... 
What's this about a bit of gumption?</font>

292
00:17:28,340 --> 00:17:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you heard the word "magic," did you 
think you'd be wielding flames or wind?</font>

293
00:17:33,710 --> 00:17:35,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know that isn't possible!</font>

294
00:17:36,390 --> 00:17:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was talking about where
your willpower comes from.</font>

295
00:17:39,210 --> 00:17:41,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could even call it your emotions...</font>

296
00:17:41,740 --> 00:17:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or a type of self-suggestion.</font>

297
00:17:44,580 --> 00:17:46,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You raise your voice. You shout.</font>

298
00:17:46,930 --> 00:17:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you stir yourself to action.</font>

299
00:17:49,310 --> 00:17:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a tremendous roar that turns
 the unreal into reality.</font>

300
00:17:52,900 --> 00:17:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's...</font>

301
00:17:54,660 --> 00:17:58,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A childish trick like that 
won't help me save everyone!</font>

302
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something like that is just...</font>

303
00:18:02,820 --> 00:18:04,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop spouting such foolishness!</font>

304
00:18:04,450 --> 00:18:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the most important 
thing of all, isn't it?</font>

305
00:18:07,270 --> 00:18:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those who cannot transform themselves</font>

306
00:18:09,540 --> 00:18:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will never change the world!</font>

307
00:18:12,370 --> 00:18:16,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's exactly what 
you're aiming to accomplish!</font>

308
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember your roots.</font>

309
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take back your origins.</font>

310
00:18:26,760 --> 00:18:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lock has already been opened.</font>

311
00:18:30,070 --> 00:18:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, take up your sword!</font>

312
00:18:33,580 --> 00:18:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's set out on a journey.</font>

313
00:18:36,490 --> 00:18:38,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over the hill of darkness...</font>

314
00:18:38,460 --> 00:18:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to pass beyond the false sky!</font>

315
00:18:50,550 --> 00:18:53,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You already know the answer!</font>

316
00:18:53,450 --> 00:18:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is the name of the magic 
that lives in your heart?</font>

317
00:19:00,540 --> 00:19:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cry out and bring it into being!</font>

318
00:19:03,380 --> 00:19:05,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is the name of your spell?!</font>

319
00:19:21,760 --> 00:19:23,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Courage!</font>

320
00:19:33,870 --> 00:19:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Limiter Off.</font>

321
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, unsheathe your sword!</font>

322
00:19:47,350 --> 00:19:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we... saved?</font>

323
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What just happened?</font>

324
00:19:58,890 --> 00:19:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just now, that...</font>

325
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be.</font>

326
00:20:04,910 --> 00:20:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is happening?</font>

327
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is...</i></font>

328
00:20:14,180 --> 00:20:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That light is vanquishing 
the monsters one after another.</i></font>

329
00:20:24,910 --> 00:20:26,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Halcon!</font>

330
00:20:35,170 --> 00:20:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sion!</font>

331
00:20:48,940 --> 00:20:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run, Sion!</font>

332
00:20:51,370 --> 00:20:53,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't... run.</font>

333
00:20:53,790 --> 00:20:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't!</font>

334
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it were him, he'd never run away!</font>

335
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That coward...</font>

336
00:21:00,710 --> 00:21:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who's braver than anyone!</font>

337
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can do this, too! 
I will not let him beat me!</font>

338
00:21:09,790 --> 00:21:11,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You have it all wrong, Sion.</i></font>

339
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was jealous. I was bitter.</i></font>

340
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was desperate.</i></font>

341
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been chasing all of you
 all this time.</i></font>

342
00:21:21,250 --> 00:21:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm just a pathetic wretch.</i></font>

343
00:21:24,220 --> 00:21:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which is why, from now on...</i></font>

344
00:21:45,150 --> 00:21:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will be like a lone sword!</i></font>

345
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#060606">Mageblade: Wis</font></b></font></font>

346
00:23:28,050 --> 00:23:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="20"><b><font color="#fffdfc">Wistoria: Wand and Sword</font></b></font></font></font>

347
00:23:36,020 --> 00:23:39,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time on <i>Wistoria: Wand and Sword</i>,</font>

348
00:23:39,150 --> 00:23:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">episode 16, "And the Story Begins."</font>

349
